comments: Ayton (POR) firms up over his left foot in Lillard's (MIL) path and does not deliver illegal contact as the screen is set.
Lillard (MIL) is moving alongside Brogdon's (POR) path when marginal body contact occurs during Brogdon's drive. Lillard then brushes Brogdon's right elbow as Brogdon elevates to pass.
Portis (MIL) moves to align himself alongside Grant's (POR) path prior to marginal contact occurring with Grant's left side during the drive.
Lillard (MIL) beats Grant (POR) to the spot and establishes a legal guarding position in Grant's path prior to Grant initiating the contact at the end of his drive.
Lopez's (MIL) hands come forward toward Grant's (POR) side and marginal contact occurs during the pick as the defensive switch simultaneously occurs.
Sharpe (POR) legally contests Beasley's (MIL) jump shot attempt.
Portis (MIL) legally contests Grant's (POR) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Portis (MIL) establishes himself in Brogdon's (POR) path and does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the pick.
Ayton (POR) turns slightly prior to marginal body contact occurring with Antetokounmpo's (MIL) side at the end of the  drive.
Henderson (POR) legally contests Lillard's (MIL) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) jumps forward prior to marginal contact occurring with Ayton's (POR) right arm and back as Ayton secures the rebound.
Ayton (POR) establishes himself in Lillard's (MIL) path and does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the pick.

Lopez (MIL) avoids making contact with Brogdon's (POR) arm as Brogdon momentarily loses control of the ball at the top of the perimeter. Lopez and Brogdon then make incidental foot contact with one another as Brogdon re-gains control.
Lopez (MIL) brings his right arm forward toward Brogdon's (POR) path and marginal contact occurs with Brogdon's front as he drives toward the lane.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) is turning and jumping away from Brogdon (POR) prior to marginal contact occurring with Brogdon's slightly extended off-arm during his driving shot attempt.
Lopez (MIL) brushes Brogdon's (POR) right arm as he gathers the ball and marginal contact occurs.

After communicating with the Replay Center, there was not clear and conclusive video evidence disputing that Brogdon's (POR) shot attempt did not make contact with the rim. The call on the floor of a shot clock violation by Portland would stand.
Henderson (POR) engages and disengages with Antetokounmpo (MIL), and marginal contact occurs as Antetokounmpo rolls toward the lane following the expiration of the pick.
Grant (POR), Ayton (POR), and Antetokounmpo (MIL) each make clean contact with the ball as simultaneous incidental contact occurs during the rebound.
Brogdon (POR) uses his forearm to cleanly dislodge the ball away from Lillard (MIL) as simultaneous incidental side-to-side contact occurs.

Brogdon (POR) uses his right forearm to make contact with the ball and the part of Antetokounmpo's (MIL) hand that is on the ball, cleanly dislodging it away from Antetokounmpo prior to incidental arm contact occurring.

Ayton (POR) contests the put-back attempt and marginal contact occurs with Antetokounmpo's (MIL) head after the release. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes contact with the ball while it is still in the imaginary cylinder above the rim following Portis' (MIL) shot attempt.

Replay review of the foul called on Antetokounmpo (MIL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Antetokounmpo cleanly blocks Brogdon's (POR) driving shot attempt and dislodges the ball prior to incidental arm contact occurring. There was not imminent possession at the time of the whistle and a jump ball at center circle was assessed.
Ayton (POR) grabs and maintains a hold of Lopez's (MIL) right arm during the jump ball.
Henderson (POR) commits a take foul on Lillard (MIL).
Ayton (POR) extends slightly as he is firming up over his right foot and he does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the screen on Connaughton (MIL) during the inbound.
Brogdon (POR) brings his right arm toward Antetokounmpo's (MIL) side and marginal contact occurs as Antetokounmpo elevates to pursue the rebound.

Henderson (POR) makes contact with the ball and the part of Antetokounmpo's (MIL) hand that is on the ball, dislodging it away from Antetokounmpo prior to incidental arm contact occurring during the rebound.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Possession is awarded to Milwaukee. However, the ball touches Antetokounmpo's (MIL) left hand last before going out of bounds. Possession should have been awarded to Portland.
Henderson (POR) commits a take foul on Lillard (MIL).
